\define next(tag) <$list filter="[tag<__tag__>after<currentTiddler>]"><$link>Next: {{!!caption}}</$link></$list>
\relink next tag

This macro creates links to the next tiddler in a tag list using its caption. Or it emits nothing if there is no next.
